data.description: Nestled in a quaint Neighborhood, this raised ranch features 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. Totaling just over 2,500 square feet, the kitchen is large with an open concept dining and living area. From room to room the home is bright and features many upgrades. On the lower level there is an oversized game room with a pellet stove for extra heating. You will also find a utility room, storage, laundry room and 2 additional rooms that can be converted to bedrooms. Access to the garage/outdoors from the lower level makes it easy to enjoy the private fenced in back yard. Only 3 minutes from AuSable Chasm and Port Kent and 20 minuets from Plattsburgh this home is a must see, schedule your tour today!
